            "DisplayOrder": 350,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 9967,
            "LocalizeKR": "뭐……뭐라고 말씀드리면\n좋을까요……",
            "LocalizeJP": "な……なんと申し上げれば\nよいのでしょう……。",
